**Question format selector** with the following types:

| Question Type | Description | Complexity |
|---|---|---|
| **Multiple Choice** | 2-6 options, single or multi-select correct | Medium |
| **True / False** | Two fixed options | Low |
| **Fill in the Blank** | Text input with or without a word bank | Medium |
| **Matching / Joining** | Connect items from two columns | High |
| **Unjumble Words** | Rearrange scrambled words into correct order | Medium |
| **Unjumble Letters** | Rearrange scrambled letters to form a word | Medium |
| **Drag & Drop to Category** | Sort items into 2+ categories | High |

