**Test data model (JSON schema):**
```javascript
{
  id: "uuid",
  title: "Unit 3 Vocabulary Test",
  description: "...",
  createdAt: timestamp,
  updatedAt: timestamp,
  settings: {
    timeLimit: 0,           // 0 = no limit, else seconds
    shuffleQuestions: true,
    shuffleOptions: true,
    showResults: true,      // show score at end
    allowRetake: false,
    collectName: true,
    collectGroup: true,
    groupOptions: ["3A", "3B", "3C", "4A", "4B", "4C", "5A", "5B", "5C", "5D"],  // NEW — default course groups
    enableFullscreen: true   // NEW — anti-cheating fullscreen mode
  },
  questions: [
    {
      id: "q-uuid",
      type: "multiple-choice",  // | "true-false" | "fill-blank" | "matching" | "unjumble-words" | "unjumble-letters" | "drag-drop-category"
      prompt: "What is the meaning of 'apple'?",
      media: {                  // optional
        type: "image",          // | "audio"
        data: "base64string",   // for local/Drive storage
        filename: "apple.jpg"
      },
      // Type-specific fields:
      options: [...],           // for MC, T/F
      correctAnswer: 0,        // index or array of indices
      multiSelect: false,       // MC: multiple correct answers
      pairs: [...],            // for matching
      blanks: [...],           // for fill-blank
      wordBank: [...],         // for fill-blank with word bank
      words: [...],            // for unjumble
      categories: [...],       // for drag-drop
      items: [...],            // for drag-drop
      points: 1                // point value
    }
  ]
}
```

**Student response data model (stored in Firebase):**
```javascript
{
  studentName: "Juan",
  group: "4B",
  answers: [...],
  score: 8,
  maxScore: 10,
  startedAt: 1709769600000,      // NEW — timestamp when test began
  completedAt: 1709770200000,    // NEW — timestamp when submitted
  durationSeconds: 600,          // NEW — elapsed time in seconds
  violations: [                  // NEW — anti-cheating log
    { type: "tab-switch", timestamp: 1709769800000 },
    { type: "fullscreen-exit", timestamp: 1709769900000 }
  ],
  violationCount: 2              // NEW — quick summary for teacher view
}
```

