#### Advanced Question Settings (per question type)

| Question Type | Advanced Settings |
|---|---|
| **Multiple Choice** | Toggle single/multi-select · Image options (each option can be an image) · Audio options (each option can be an audio clip) · Custom number of options (2-6) |
| **True / False** | Custom labels (e.g., "Correct/Incorrect" instead of "True/False") |
| **Fill in the Blank** | Toggle word bank on/off · Case-sensitive matching toggle · Accept multiple correct answers |
| **Matching** | Number of pairs (3-8) · Shuffle right column |
| **Unjumble** | Show hint (first letter) toggle |
| **Drag & Drop** | Number of categories (2-4) · Allow items to belong to multiple categories |

