## Implementation Phases & Effort Estimate

| Phase | Scope | Files | Est. Implementation Size |
|---|---|---|---|
| **Phase 1** | Builder UI + all 7 question types + preview | `test-builder.html`, `css/test-builder.css`, `js/test-builder.js`, [tools.html](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Documents/esl-learning-platform/tools.html) | Large (~2000-3000 lines) |
| **Phase 2** | Media uploads + advanced settings per type | Extends Phase 1 files | Medium (~500-800 lines) |
| **Phase 3** | Student-facing test page + sharing via code/link/QR | `take-test.html`, `css/take-test.css`, `js/take-test.js`, [firebase-service.js](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Documents/esl-learning-platform/js/firebase-service.js) | Large (~1500-2500 lines) |
| **Phase 4** | Response collection dashboard + CSV export + Google Sheets hook | Extends builder + Firebase | Medium (~500-800 lines) |

**Total estimated:** ~5000-7000 lines of new code across 6 new files and 2 modified files.

